                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-49-off293 t18130714-49-cd294"></join>, a watch, value 4 l. and a watch-key, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130714-49-victim553" type="victimName">
                     Roger 
                     M'Donald
                  <interp inst="t18130714-49-victim553" type="surname" value="M'Donald"></interp>
